TCS,Cloud,Messaging,Center,REST,API,allows,developers,to,easily,integrate,text,messaging,into,their,applications,and,web,services,for,building,automation,business,continuity,alerts,and,notifications,We,offer,two,way,text,messaging,coverage,on,all,US,wireless,carriers,network,The,Cloud,Messaging,Center,CMC,REST,API,provides,a,set,of,methods,that,are,called,using,https,or,http,to,perform,messaging,SMS,features,such,as,Sending,a,message,Getting,delivery,receipts,Replying,to,a,message,Creating,contacts,and,groups,Scheduling,messages